title: Complete Texas Chainsaw Massacre Comics Collection [June 2014]
description:
The SHAREGO torrent already uploaded is dead and missing many comics. I mean, there's one seed, but no ones connecting and everyone is stuck at 86%.


So.


I took the liberty of going through some of my data dvds and found that I already had an almost complete collection that just took about an hour of hard internet digging to finish off. So please enjoy and hope everyone has a great weekend.















RIP Casey Kasem (Shaggy)
RIP Magazine3k
